White River SPCA treasurer, Estelle de Villiers said they made R2 000 at its car boot sale at Casterbridge Lifestyle Centre.  The White River SPCA started the sale three years ago, with just three cars at the time, but has grown in its numbers over the past few years.  ALSO READ: IN PHOTOS: 3D Archery in the Lowveld  ALSO READ: KLCBT developing new tourism website